flowchart TD
    A[User Input] --> B[Context Collection]

    B --> C[Load Project Memory]
    C --> D[Search Codebase (grep/tools)]

    D --> E[Assemble System Prompt]
    E --> F[Add Tool Constraints]

    F --> G[Plan Task (Agent Reasoning)]
    G --> H[Break into Subtasks]

    H --> I[Call Tools / Execute Steps]
    I --> J[Update Memory]

    J --> K[Refine Output]
    K --> L[Final Prompt to Model]

    L --> M[Response to User]